\c 84
\s Mufaro uri paimba yaMwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weGititi. Pisarema ravanakomana vaKora.
\p
\v 1 Ugaro hwenyu hunodikanwa sei, Imi Jehovha wehondo!
\v 2 Mweya wangu unoshuva, zvirokwazvo unopanga vazhe dzaJehovha; Mwoyo wangu nenyama yangu zvinodana kuna Mwari mupenyu.
\v 3 Zvirokwazvo, shiri yakazviwanira imba, Nyenganyenga yakazviwanira dendere, painoisa vana vayo, Ipo paaritari dzenyu, Jehovha wehondo, Mambo wangu, naMwari wangu.
\v 4 Vakaropafadzwa vanogara mumba menyu; Vachagara vachikurumbidzai.
\v 5 Akaropafadzwa munhu ane simba rake mamuri; Anemigwagwa inoenda Zioni mumwoyo make.
\p
\v 6 Kana vachipfuura nomumupata wakaoma,
\s vanouita nzvimbo inamatsime; Zvirokwazvo, mvura yomunhuruka
\s imutukULa nemiksombomo.
\p
\v 7 Vanowedzera simba pasimba ravo, Mumwe nomumwe wavo anosvika pamberi paMwari paZioni.
\p
\v 8 Haiwa, Jehovha wehondo, inzwa munyengetero wangu;
\p Tererai nenzeve, Mwari waJakobho.
\v 9 Tarirai, Mwari, nhoo yedu,
\s Muone chiso chomuzodzwa wenyu.
\p
\v 1 Â° Nokuti zuva rimwe pavazhe dzenyu rinokunda mamwe ane chiuru
\s pakunaka.
\s Ndinoti zviri nani kuti ndive murindi
\s womukova mumba maMwari wangu,
\s Pakuti ndigare pamatende avane zvakaipa.
\s "Nokuti Jehovha Mwari izuva nenhoo;
\s Jehovha achapa nyasha nokukudzwa;
\s Hapana chinhu chakanaka chaanganyima
\s vanofamba nokururama.
\p
\v 12 Jehovha wehondo,
\s Akaropafadzwa munhu anovimba nemi.
